OL,3,CWhat happens if the largest party in
OL,4,CSenedd election falls short of a
OL,5,Cmajority?
OL,7,FBy Sharp End producer Guto Llewelyn
OL,9,FThe Senedd election is little more
OL,10,Fthan a fortnight away and our latest
OL,11,Fpoll suggests we're in for a
OL,12,Fremarkably tight contest.
OL,14,FIt's 12 months since Plaid Cymru first
OL,15,Ftopped an ITV Wales/YouGov poll, and
OL,16,Fsince then they have received the most
OL,17,Fsupport in every poll we have
OL,18,Fcommissioned.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
