OL,3,CWhat happens if the largest party in
OL,4,CSenedd election falls short of a
OL,5,Cmajority?
OL,7,FIt may trigger a few jitters within
OL,8,FPlaid Cymru, who were 14 points ahead
OL,9,Fof Reform UK in our January poll. For
OL,10,FReform UK, this poll gives them
OL,11,Fserious cause for optimism, with the
OL,12,Fclock ticking to polling day.
OL,14,FBut there's more to this poll than
OL,15,Fjust the headline figures and seat
OL,16,Fprojections. By taking a deeper dive,
OL,17,Fwe can find fascinating clues as to
OL,18,Fthe mindset of the Welsh electorate.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
